name: How Do Ya Pronounce Your Pronouns?

metadata.name: "How Do Ya Pronounce Your Pronouns?"
metadata.description:
All caught up in a path of resistance,  
Comfort zones killing conditioned kids,  
Pushing change in an instance,  
Creating rules and words to give them more options, 
In their bullying schemes,  
Blinding schools, parents, 
Entities controlling dreams,  
False demonic beliefs,  
Stealing souls,  
Worse than the common thief,  
Am I one forced to rectify a shadowed world,  
To lift the veil,  
Show whats underneath,  
No sush, yet discreet,  
They might never see,  
But they sure are guaranteed to meet,  
No matter, what?..
